2105: Synthetic City Soundscape is a compilation of futuristic music inspired by the 80's with a little touch of modern electronic composition. The pack consists of various pieces, atmospheric ambients, club themes, sad and epic heroic tracks, sad and epic not-so-heroic tracks, and armored-shotgun-wielding-men themes of course.

But there's more. You will be getting all the possible seamless loops, so you can actually construct your own composition if needed. There's even a possibility that some parts of different tracks will be matching perfectly, don't know, we've never tried. Should you need more assistance in production of music, please feel free to contact us any time.
